<br>
We usually tell clerics and enchanters to bring their own reagents. Then we collect the reagent fees from all attendees except those who use reagents. The money from the reagents is then redistributed to those who use reagents based on how many they use during the raid (honor system of course). It's entirely up to the raid leader how to handle this. <br>
<br>
